<h2> Chapter One Story</h2></br>
Chapter One starts with the <a href="/monsters/protagonist.html">Protagonist</a> wandering desert dunes.</br></br>
<i id="dessert">Setting: Sand</br></br>
Trigger: Movement to certain area</br>
Result: Monsters appear to fight the protagonist</br></br>
~Start basic fighting tutorial~</br></br>
Trigger: 25% Monsters Defeated</br>
Result: Sandstorm Appears</br></br></i>
While moving forward, cliff walls (of which the protagonist is at the bottom)</br>
come together and force the protagonist to a certain area.</br></br>
<i>Trigger: Movement to certain area</br>
Result: Sandstorm lessens(still obscures distant vision, but other side of arena is somewhat visible)</br></br></i>
You keep going forward.</br></br>
<i id="sand_arena"> Setting: The walls widen out to form a large circle(arena).</br>
The sand is blown down from the right slope. It is piled up in the ____ side of the circle.</br>
The right wall slopes out steeply(about 75 degrees out of circle), with holes(windows) in the side.</br>
As the wall goes around the circle, it slopes into the circle (about 80 degrees) on the left.</br></br></i>
Explore the area.


</br></br>
